      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "The drake can exhale a blast of condiments in one of three forms: mustard spray, ketchup blast, or relish mist. Each form is a 60-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 16 Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 28 (4d6 + 14) damage and suffers the effect associated with the chosen condiment. On a successful save, the creature takes half as much damage and suffers no condition. Once the drake uses one of the forms, it can't use another form until the next recharge. The drake can't use Condiment Breath again until it recharges."
